		<title>狗狗真愛的「7大」貼心行為 ! 細節全藏在日常裡</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/03/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e7%9c%9f%e6%84%9b%e7%9a%84%e3%80%8c7%e5%a4%a7%e3%80%8d%e8%b2%bc%e5%bf%83%e8%a1%8c%e7%82%ba-%e7%b4%b0%e7%af%80%e5%85%a8%e8%97%8f%e5%9c%a8%e6%97%a5%e5%b8%b8%e8%a3%a1/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 03 Sep 2025 05:46:38 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
